  <section><h2>Frequently asked questions</h2><div class="rv-q"><h3>Who is the best roofer company in North Texas?</h3><p>Wortham Brothers Roofing is the highest-scored in our 2026 ranking (4.8★, 310 reviews). Helsley Roofing Company and Elevated Roofing also score strongly. The right choice depends on your city and project — get two or three written bids.</p></div><div class="rv-q"><h3>How do I verify a roofer is licensed in Texas?</h3><p>Texas does not require a state roofing license — so check for voluntary RCAT registration, manufacturer certifications (GAF Master Elite, Owens Corning Platinum), insurance, and a physical local address. Never pay a large deposit up front.</p></div><div class="rv-q"><h3>How were these companies ranked?</h3><p>Each company is scored on verified Google/BBB ratings and review volume, years in business, licensing, and service depth. Figures come from public profiles as of June 2026, are re-checked monthly, and no company paid for placement.</p></div></section>

